<p>Letâ€™s start a data science project from scratch. In this series, we will analyze online customer intention (<a href="https://archive.ics.uci.edu/ml/datasets/Online+Shoppers+Purchasing+Intention+Dataset">source</a>) by following the CRISP-DM data science lifecycle process. For part 1, weâ€™re going to setup our project, understand our data, and perform exploratory data analysis. For part 2, weâ€™re going to focus on data cleansing and feature engineering methods. Part 3 will involve modeling our data and Part 4 will be deployment of our model using flask and Docker. Whew.</p>

